title: Rolling Stones - Out Of Our Heads US + UK (2005)  [24-88 HD FLAC
description:
Out of Our Heads is the Rolling Stones' third British album and their fourth in the United States. It was released in 1965 with significant track listing differences between territories. The US edition includes the first album release of "(I Can't Get No) Satisfaction" - one of the all-time greatest rock songs ever recorded. In 2004, Rolling Stone magazine placed "Satisfaction" in the second spot on its list of "The 500 Greatest Songs of All Time", while in 2006 it was added to the Library of Congress National Recording Registry. In 2005 ABKCO Records re-relased both original mono editions of Out Of Our Heads in remastered 24bit audio HD.
